    <p
      class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400 sm:leading-7 lg:leading-8 sm:text-base lg:text-lg"
    >
      <strong>What is a holistic software engineer?</strong> I focus on the entire
      software development lifecycle, from understanding user needs and designing
      intuitive interfaces to writing clean, efficient code and ensuring smooth deployment
      and maintenance. I believe that great software is built not just through coding,
      but through a deep understanding of the problem space and a commitment to delivering
