    >
      It was my shot to fame! I was part of a Guiness World Record for taking part in the world's largest Game Jam held at the University of Bedfordshire. 
      While everyone else were rehashing a set of supplied game assets and boilerplate code, I decided to go all out and build a game from scratch, using WPF and C#. Mainly because my friend was more familiar with it than C++. 
